Create Folder Structure

On your local machine or EC2:

mkdir python
pip install pymysql -t python/

Very important:
The folder name MUST be python


Zip It
zip -r pymysql_layer.zip python

Create Layer in AWS

Go to:

Lambda → Layers → Create Layer

Upload:

pymysql_layer.zip

Attach Layer to Lambda

Go to:

Lambda → Your Function → Layers → Add Layer
Select:

netmaze-pymysql-layer
